Class DefaultHttpParameters

    public class DefaultHttpParameters
extends io.netty.handler.codec.DefaultHeaders<java.lang.String,java.lang.String,HttpParameters>
implements HttpParameters
    Default implementation of HttpParameters which uses the HashingStrategy.JAVA_HASHER to support case-sensitive parameter names.
